positive.review: Surprisingly solid and still one of the best entries in the series. The match engine is stable, the UI is clean, and team management feels deep without being overwhelming. Highly recommended.
Peakk

Just cant afford a better laptop to get the newer games.
love the fact i can guide my favourite team towards the future and try make them win
